+/*
+ *  Technologic Systems TS-72XX sbc /proc/driver/sbcinfo entry.
+ *
+ *  Original idea by Liberty Young (Technologic Systems).
+ *
+ *	(c) Copyright 2008  Matthieu Crapet <mcrapet@gmail.com>
